abstract: Also try vegan cacio e pepe, spicy white bean stew and more recipes.
lead_paragraph: The week’s most popular dishes included some vegetarian heavy hitters, like Melissa Clark’s mushroom Bourguignon (above), Alexa Weibel’s vegan cacio e pepe, and Alison Roman’s spicy white bean stew with broccoli rabe. Find more recipes in the collection below.
